OL,6,FWhich?'s February consumer insight
OL,7,Ftracker - weighted to be nationally
OL,8,Frepresentative with approximately
OL,9,F2,000 respondents - found that these
OL,10,Fcosts remain a huge concern as eight
OL,11,Fin 10 (79%) said they were worried
OL,12,Fabout food prices.
OL,14,FOther data shows that 8% have
OL,15,Fprioritised meals for other family
OL,16,Fmembers and 3% have turned to food
OL,17,Fbanks.
