OL,4,Camid cost of food crisis
OL,6,FThe average price of pasta and
OL,7,Fcouscous was up 10.8% in the year to
OL,8,FJanuary compared with a rise of 6.6%
OL,9,Fin the year to December, while fruit
OL,10,Fand vegetable juices were up 12.2%
OL,11,Fcompared with 10.4%, according to
OL,12,FConsumer Prices Index (CPI) data
OL,13,Fpublished by the Office for National
OL,14,FStatistics (ONS).
OL,16,FTwo food staples have also seen
OL,17,Finflation quicken: eggs, up 7.2% in
OL,18,FJanuary compared with a rise of 6.8%
OL,19,Fin December, and yoghurt, up 9.9%
OL,20,Fcompared with 8.6%.
