OL,3,COne in eight households skipping meals
OL,4,Camid cost of food crisis
OL,6,FThe figures come as an estimated 1.9
OL,7,Fmillion households missed or defaulted
OL,8,Fon at least one mortgage, rent, loan,
OL,9,Fcredit card or bill in the month to
OL,10,FFebruary 7.
OL,12,FThis is significantly lower than the
OL,13,Fmonth to January 12 - which saw 2.4
OL,14,Fmillion households miss payments - but
OL,15,Freflects the high missed payment rates
OL,16,Fseen throughout the cost of living
OL,17,Fcrisis.
