OL,3,COne in eight households skipping meals
OL,4,Camid cost of food crisis
OL,6,FIn Wales, Which? found the highest
OL,7,Fconcentration of areas at high risk
OL,8,Fduring the food crisis in the Valleys,
OL,9,Fwhere people are more likely to be
OL,10,Fsuffering from fuel poverty and on a
OL,11,Flow income.
OL,13,FIn Scotland, the places in highest
OL,14,Fneed of support are in the Central
OL,15,FBelt, but there is also a notable
OL,16,Fconcentration in and around Dundee.
OL,18,FIn Northern Ireland, there is a
OL,19,Fnoticeably greater concentration in
OL,20,Fparts of south west Belfast and in and
OL,21,Faround Derry/Londonderry.
